    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction is accepted for submission and regulatory review under the Minimal profile. All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been evaluated; 7 factors are assessed with documented achieved and required levels, and 6 factors are formally flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps at Model Risk Level 5. The overall decision on model adequacy remains Not Accepted pending resolution of the identified gaps, but the assessment package itself is accepted as a complete and transparent characterization of the current credibility state.",
